N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8124.26 - Town of York

State Regulations
(a) Retsof Road
from Route 63 to a point 0.2+- mile south of Route 63; provided, however, that
this route is designated as an access highway for use by tractor-semitrailer
combinations with no overall length limitations and for vehicles 102 inches
wide, and is not hereby designated as an access highway for tandem trailer
vehicles. Notes
